    <item>
      <title>埃及总理称与国际货币基金组织的谈判旨在延长贷款措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/egypt-s-talks-with-imf-aim-to-prolong-loan-measures-pm-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及总理穆斯塔法·马德布利周三表示，埃及与国际货币基金组织的谈判旨在延长该国 80 亿美元贷款计划所要求的措施的实施，而不是为了获得更多资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/egypt-s-talks-with-imf-aim-to-prolong-loan-measures-pm-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 13:40:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
